{"tid":367446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聲援良心犯】支援被捕者 捐款塞爆籌款箱","createTime":"2017-08-20T17:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T17:18:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"134ba523f18fbe73c82808e071aebef74dcc015a","tid":367446,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170821/large/1503247599_e1aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170821%2Flarge%2F1503247599_e1aa.jpg&h=beaf19e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170821/57106507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170821%2F57106507&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3Lk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c4637bd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170821%2F57106507&h=2f0b594a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170821/57106507</a><br />\n<br />\n不少遊行人士昨聲援在囚抗爭者之餘，更踴躍捐款。現場所見，印有東北支援組、社民連、香港眾志及大專政改關注組四個組織標誌的籌款箱，被捐款塞爆，內有不少500元及100元紙幣。社民連主席吳文遠表示，今次籌款無分政黨，是統一以大會名義籌款，款項用作支援被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有大會義工所有籌款箱都被捐款塞爆，時事評論員潘小濤指「喺遊行時有咁多人捐錢，今次真係前所未見，不過唔夠嘅，最好開放眾籌戶口！」"},{"pid":"94546e4826bc33ee80eb3310331986edd07249e1","tid":367446,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"點解每次都要籌款？極討厭"},{"pid":"3c2bff5335f7b162a43a82e28d71f31722dc9cde","tid":367446,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解每次都要籌款？極討厭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比義士上訴架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6f76c4e576c9077d37ed8c46870c31d0b406aa","tid":367446,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"草船行動大成功！"}]